\section{Summary}
\small
Fullstack Engineer with 7+ years building high-scale event-driven systems — TypeScript/Node.js, React/Next.js, autonomous LLM agent workflows, and data pipelines serving millions of users. I default to action, prototype and productionize rapidly using lean experimentation and feature flags — concept to production in hours, not sprints. Strong instincts for observability, reliability, and closing feedback loops between systems and business outcomes.

