  \item Shipped an autonomous LLM agent workflow that researches, reasons, and personalizes learning paths per user — orchestrated multi-step decisioning and content delivery across Next.js frontend and FastAPI backend using LangChain and OpenAI
  \item Built data ingestion pipeline transforming raw course content into indexed context for AI-driven recommendations — sub-second retrieval latency at query time
  \item Built customer-facing dashboard translating LLM agent operations into actionable insights — reduced time for users to understand personalized recommendations from minutes to seconds
  \item Prototyped and productionized rapidly using lean experimentation — iterated from concept to working agent pipeline in days using feature flags and incremental rollouts
  \item Closed the feedback loop with end-to-end observability — logging, tracing, and performance metrics fed back into agent behavior, creating a self-optimizing system that improved recommendation relevance continuously
\end{itemize}

\vspace{4pt}
